[00:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Open your eyes. To a whole new dimension. The world\'s first 360 drone: Antigravity A1 Exceptionally lightweight.'

[00:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'With immersive Vision goggles and an intuitive Grip controller. The sky is in your command. Top and bottom dual lenses deliver 360-degree clarity, with 8K resolution.'

[00:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Replaceable lenses help push your limits. So you never stop exploring. Featherweight Vision goggles offer premium, 1-inch micro OLED displays.'

[00:45] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Pulling you right into the moment. With 360-degree details. Look anywhere. See everything. Immerse yourself completely.'

[00:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'This is flight like never before. Climb incredible heights and soar with the thrill of a bird’s-eye view. No piloting skills?'

[01:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'No problem. A1 offers two types of motion control. Just point, and go. Designed to feel natural Flight guided by instinct. Watch the world open up.'

[01:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Pure freedom in motion. Share the experience with Sky Path. Simply set the path, And let A1 take the lead.'

[01:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Fully autonomous flight. Share breathtaking, jaw-dropping moments. Or turn flight into something magical.'

[01:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Sky Genie turns every move into a cinematic moment. Flip the focus.'

[02:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Spiral deep into space. A1 captures it all. While traditional drones demand near-perfect aim. Enjoy the action, frame it later. Never miss the shot.'

[02:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Create endless stories with just one take. Use Auto Edit to find highlights for you. Build seamless transitions.'

[02:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Get smooth cinematic results, completely automatic. Level up your flights even further.'

[02:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'With one tap, lock onto your subject. Stay with them through every dynamic move. Utilize our intelligent obstacle avoidance,'

[03:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'combined with Navigation Assist, so you always know what\'s ahead. Plus a payload detection system, stopping flight if extra weight is detected.'

[03:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Two battery options to keep you airborne. Fly up to 39 minutes. Transmission up to 10km in full 360. Go beyond. Capture further.'

[03:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Stretch your horizons, bend your world, dive into an ocean of creative possibilities. Back home, relive every moment in 8K,'

[03:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'watch the edges fade into open sky. Your sky. Your rules.'

[03:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'This is not just a drone. This is a revolution in flight.'
